License:		GNU General Public License version 2 or later; see LICENSE.txt

1. Copyright and disclaimer
---------------------------
This application is opensource software released under the GPL.  Please
see source code and the LICENSE file


2. Changelog
------------
This is a non-exhaustive (but still near complete) changelog for
Joomla! 1.6, including alpha and beta versions.
Our thanks to all those people who've contributed bug reports and
code fixes.

Legend:

* -> Security Fix
# -> Bug Fix
$ -> Language fix or change
+ -> Addition
^ -> Change
- -> Removed
! -> Note

03-May-2010 Andrew Eddie
 ^ Merge fixes to media fields (Elin Waring)
 + Merge addition of featured contacts view (Elin Waring)
 + Merge extra fields for user profile plugin (Elin Waring)
 ^ Merge various fixes to HTML filtering of and buttons of rich textareas (Elin Waring)
 ^ Merge changes/fixes to sample data: fruit shop style fix; articles category module (Elin Waring)

2-May-2010 Christophe Demko
# Correcting a bug I have introduced on commit #16536

