$ Consolidating some categories, contact, newsfeeds, weblinks,content strings
$ Refactoring com_contacts frontend ini/keys
$ Added calendar image in front-end (Thanks Bill)
$ Moving icons for com_contact to new folder in media/contacts/images/
$ Correcting/consolidating strings
^ Adding fax in contact edit
# Correcting mod_banners [20301](thanks Phil Snell)

